{
  "stem": "7781.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We crossed the Elba, but they provide-- the American provide transportation, and-- and we landed in Lynnebrook.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know where we'd take us to Lynnebrook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it happened, they took us to Lynnebrook, to an English army camp, where English soldiers were stationed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they quartered us in this camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this camp was a good camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was this a DP camp?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was an American army camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had part, a transient camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, they had--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For people who were immigrating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For people that were displaced, they would keep them there until transport was available.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would send them-- we had French-- former French prisoners of war, the Italians, and you had there from all over, prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they kept them there till transport was available.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You send them back to their countries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were landed in this camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this camp was a good camp, because the food was excellent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The English behaved very nice towards us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came and-- to this camp, and the soldiers helped us take off the luggage, you know, and-- and I watched the luggage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those three went into a-- they were ordered to go into a building, you know, the-- the German army camps, they had those red buildings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was watching the luggage, whatever we had, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The-- they came out with cots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, I don't know what the cots were for at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I suppose-- and-- and then they took the luggage and said we should into the building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As we walked in the building, there was an English soldier handing out cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, a card.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he walked up-- they made us go up on the second floor, the third.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
